OL,3,CWoman shot by husband on Valentine's
OL,4,CDay after trying to escape relationship
OL,6,FA woman was shot and killed by her
OL,7,Fhusband outside a pub in a Kent
OL,8,Fvillage on Valentine's Day after
OL,9,Ftrying to flee the relationship, an
OL,10,Finquest heard.
OL,12,FLisa Smith, 43, was shot twice in the
OL,13,Fneck in the car park of The Three
OL,14,FHorseshoes on Main Road in Knockholt,
OL,15,Fon February 14 this year.
OL,17,FShe had told her sister she was
OL,18,Fleaving her husband Edward Smith
OL,19,Fearlier that day, and had got on a
OL,20,Ftrain from their home in Slough, to
OL,21,Fstay with family in Kent.
