OL,3,CWoman shot by husband on Valentine's
OL,4,CDay after trying to escape relationship
OL,6,FHe tracked her down at the pub that
OL,7,Fevening before blocking their car with
OL,8,Fhis and firing four shots with a
OL,9,Fhandgun, Kent and Medway Coroner's
OL,10,FCourt heard.
OL,12,FOn Wednesday, Area Coroner Katrina
OL,13,FHepburn concluded Ms Smith died from
OL,14,Funlawful killing and found "requisite
OL,15,Fintent from Edward Smith to kill her
OL,16,For cause her really serious harm".
