OL,3,CWoman shot by husband on Valentine's
OL,4,CDay after trying to escape relationship
OL,6,FAfter killing his wife, Mr Smith, also
OL,7,Fknown as Edvard Stockings, sent voice
OL,8,Fnotes to someone he called "Nana"
OL,9,Fsaying "I've shot Lisa she's dead"
OL,10,Fbefore he was seen to jump to his
OL,11,Fdeath from the Queen Elizabeth II
OL,12,Fbridge in Dartford later that evening,
OL,13,Fthe court heard.
OL,15,FIn one of the voice notes he said
OL,16,F"hopefully I'm going to get into
OL,17,Fheaven with my wife" after alluding to
OL,18,Fsuicide.
