OL,3,CWoman shot by husband on Valentine's
OL,4,CDay after trying to escape relationship
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant James Dolby told
OL,7,Fthe court that Ms Smith was picked up
OL,8,Fat Orpington station by her friends
OL,9,Fand sister shortly before they went to
OL,10,Fthe Horseshoe Pub.
OL,12,FJust before 7pm, Ms Smith was in the
OL,13,Fpassenger seat of her friend Nancy's
OL,14,FSeat in the pub car park when her
OL,15,Fhusband arrived, having called her and
OL,16,Fher friends multiple times while
OL,17,Flooking for her.
