OL,3,CWoman shot by husband on Valentine's
OL,4,CDay after trying to escape relationship
OL,6,FThere was a "verbal altercation"
OL,7,Fbetween him and Ms Smith's sister
OL,8,FLaura who called him a "narcissist"
OL,9,Finside the pub, he got back in his car
OL,10,Fand left.
OL,12,FMr Dolby said: "At 18.59 Nancy
OL,13,Freverses her Seat onto Harrow Road and
OL,14,Fstops to speak with Laura.
OL,16,F"Edward manoeuvres his vehicle to stop
OL,17,FNancy from exiting ... Effectively
OL,18,FEdward has blocked them in."
