OL,3,CWoman shot by husband on Valentine's
OL,4,CDay after trying to escape relationship
OL,6,FThe first two shots from his handgun
OL,7,Fwere fired from inside his own
OL,8,Fvehicle, the court heard.
OL,10,FThe coroner said: "He pulled forward
OL,11,Fin the car and fired a second shot, he
OL,12,Fwas seen to exit the vehicle with arms
OL,13,Foutstretched holding a handgun and
OL,14,Ffiring a shot through the drivers side
OL,15,Fcar window."
OL,17,FIt was this third shot that caused
OL,18,F"fatal damage" to Ms Smith's neck,
OL,19,Fbefore he came around to the passenger
OL,20,Fside and fired at her again from close
OL,21,Frange.
