OL,6,F"Four shots were fired, the first two
OL,7,Ffrom within his vehicle towards the
OL,8,FSeat.
OL,10,F"There were no injuries consistent
OL,11,Fwith the trajectory of those first two
OL,12,Fbullets," said Ms Hepburn.
OL,14,FOn Wednesday morning, Ms Smith's
OL,15,Ffather asked the detective why they
OL,16,Fhad not driven away after the first
OL,17,Ftwo shots.
OL,19,F"You'd have started up and gone,
OL,20,Fwouldn't you?" he asked.
