OL,6,F"It happened very quickly," Mr Dolby
OL,7,Fexplained.
OL,9,FDespite CPR from members of the public
OL,10,Fand emergency services, Ms Smith died
OL,11,Ffrom her injuries at 19.42.
OL,13,FSetting out her conclusion, the
OL,14,Fcoroner said: "I am satisfied on the
OL,15,Fbalance of probabilities that a short
OL,16,Fform conclusion of unlawful killing
OL,17,Fwould be safe and appropriate to set
OL,18,Fout in this manner.
